    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition and is best suited for buyers who are mechanically inclined, looking for a project car, or need basic transportation on a very tight budget. The engine starts but runs roughly, exhibiting noticeable hesitation and occasional misfires. The transmission shifts with some difficulty, and there are mechanical issues that will require attention before this vehicle can be considered fully reliable. The body shows significant wear including rust, dents, and faded paint, and the interior is worn with torn upholstery and non-functional features. This car is being sold as-is, and buyers should budget for repairs beyond the purchase price. A pre-purchase mechanical inspection is strongly encouraged.",
