      "description": "Looking for an ultra-budget ride to get you from point A to point B? This vehicle is priced to move and offers an affordable entry point for drivers on a tight budget! Be aware: this car is in poor condition, meaning it has visible wear, cosmetic issues, and may require some mechanical attention. It's best suited for a handy buyer or someone comfortable taking on a project \u2014 but at this price, the value is hard to beat!",
