    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 **Budget-Friendly Fixer or Parts Car \u2014 Priced to Reflect Its Condition!** Looking for an affordable entry-level option or a project vehicle? Here's your chance! We'll be straight with you: this car is in poor condition, showing significant wear, and will likely need some meaningful repairs to get it performing at its best. There are visible issues that any honest inspection will reveal, so we've priced it accordingly \u2014 no surprises! If you're a handy DIYer, a mechanic looking for a project, or simply need basic transportation on a tight budget, this could be the right fit. Come take a look and see if it works for you!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
