      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and makes for a dependable, practical choice for everyday driving. The exterior presents well, with only minor surface scuffs and light wear consistent with normal use \u2014 nothing that detracts significantly from its overall appearance. The interior is clean and comfortable, with upholstery and trim showing modest signs of regular use but no major damage or odors. Mechanically, the car runs reliably and has been maintained to a reasonable standard, making it a solid used vehicle for a buyer seeking quality transportation without paying mint-condition prices.",
